title: Rasputina - Complete Discography
description:
This is the complete discography of Rasputina containing all their studio albums, live recordings and EPs up to 2008:

(1996) Thanks for the Ether
(1997) Transylvanian Regurgitations
(1998) How We Quit the Forest
(2001) The Lost & Found (1st Edition)
(2002) Cabin Fever
(2002) My Fever Broke
(2003) The Lost & Found (2nd Edition)
(2004) Frustration Plantation
(2005) A Radical Recital
(2007) Oh Perilous World

All the tracks are tagged properly and all the first tracks contain the album cover. Enjoy and seed.
